NY Night Train SOUL CLAP & DANCE-OFF with DJs Jonathan Toubin and Kid Congo Powers! Live Wolfmanhattan Project (Kid Congo, Mick Collins, and Bob Bert! Official debut!), Olivia Neutron John, PMS & The Moodswings

Shake a tail feather all night long when the world’s most popular and prolific soul party hits the Bowery Ballroom for an action packed night of live music and dancing! DJ Jonathan Toubin turn’s his big bad o.g.1960s soul vinyl dynamite accompanied by the fabulous NY Night Train Shadow Dancers ‘til 2AM! Get in the $100 Midnight Dance Contest with DJ Kid Congo Powers and a distinguished panel of judges! 

11:30PM – 2AM: dance party with DJ Jonathan Toubin and the NYNT Shadow Dancers

MIDNIGHT: $100 Dance-Off with DJ Kid Congo Powers

10:30PM The Wolfmanhattan Project

9:30PM Olivia Neutron John

8:30PM PMS & The Mood Swings

$14 entry before 11pm, $7 entry after 11pm
